metadata.name: #82 CLOWN PRINCE
metadata.description:
CLOWN PRINCE is a very strange looking Homie and is never seen without his makeup- because it is tattooed onto his face. He owns and operates the local tattoo parlor called The Tattoo Palace, where he reigns as prince. He is known throughout the Southwest as the baddest tattoo artist on the streets, and even though his rates are expensive, Homies will wait months to get ink rom him.
